verbose_text: For example, knockdown of the zinc finger protein snail increases the sensitivity of A549 cells to cisplatin [XREF_BIBR], and inhibition of ZNF746 suppressed invasive activities and blocked the epithelial to mesenchymal transition in H460 non small cell lung cancer cells [XREF_BIBR].
